{"tid":767662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣富二代炒車女友亡 答應冥婚後反悔 民俗專家：恐厲鬼纏身","createTime":"2018-08-04T16:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T18:14:59.000Z","uid":22349,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fae05dddb75d2a19c5bfdb573f00ff1067544ce3","tid":767662,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"台北某集團的游姓「富二代」，上月初揸跑車載劉姓的女友兜風時在隧道自炒，導致劉女慘死當場。游男事後表示願與劉女進行冥婚，惟不久後以「擔心女友無法投胎」為由反悔。有民俗專家接受台媒訪問時反駁游男的說法，又指其許下承諾後出爾反爾，恐怕會遭化為厲鬼的劉女糾纏。<br />\n<br />\n民俗專家指出，習俗中的冥婚是用死者「三魂」中的「凡間魂」來供生者迎娶，而死者的「地府魂」則會去投胎。在台灣，冥婚通常會將錢、女方遺物裝在利是封內，再放在路邊讓有緣的男性執拾，「被喜歡上了若不妥協，恐怕會有危險」。<br />\n<br />\n該民俗專家又指，游男與劉女本已到了談婚論嫁的地步，在劉女過身之後，游男又再次許諾會迎娶對方，「被娶進去祂（劉女）已經知道了，那你現在等於要退婚，那我們的面子要拿到哪鎮裏去，所以她會變成厲鬼，會變成更兇惡，你為甚麼要耍我？」"},{"pid":"8c94c1eb33f542a77c96a7ed89448893b3403fe8","tid":767662,"uid":149566,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T16:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下世小心啲"},{"pid":"bc13950df816acdca0bd43754d0500f01dbce364","tid":767662,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人鬼情未了"},{"pid":"a08f06344b1e5188c3dd8d639828578cbe713f70","tid":767662,"uid":82068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:10:47.000Z","msg":"如果比南亞人撿到會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d92c92b15b805f5564c964796a226fa7c0af93e","tid":767662,"uid":45332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a08f06344b1e5188c3dd8d639828578cbe713f70","tid":767662,"uid":82068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:10:47.000Z","msg":"如果比南亞人撿到會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:12:43.000Z","msg":"應該會多謝哂，佢哋一夫多妻，多你一個唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f714e98bb5210951a2e905a010e3fd7471a7e14","tid":767662,"uid":142233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:14:52.000Z","msg":"點解死者家人要執著搞冥婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06dcfcfb8c2503402234921607fed38d19e361e2","tid":767662,"uid":55519,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:15:44.000Z","msg":"痴線 放路邊陰鳩人姐 你同個個人有仇真係可以咁做"},{"pid":"a030137efe67e7cc9ea8ea6257560f73a20922a9","tid":767662,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:16:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96872fdab232edef9d08c64f9984ccd138602cc9","tid":767662,"uid":1880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:23:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴線 放路邊陰鳩人姐 你同個個人有仇真係可以咁做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇wiki話女方要比嫁妝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後放個神主牌上下香就得"},{"pid":"7b079dc137d97bdd3f2caa16957bd7e9eb5ce5af","tid":767662,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:31:16.000Z","msg":"被個富二代車死左自己仲要做鬼都要嫁去個殺人兇手到，我都係快快投胎算啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2fca9af52746642fcaf87e8f673fed51c9da9e3","tid":767662,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:33:48.000Z","msg":"$$$$"},{"pid":"b47961a94e825cde20ea959a6e0afa26d4717533","tid":767662,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:34:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/M1R3Kq1ATYQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FM1R3Kq1ATYQ&d=y9yaBAkfFwqnobs0iwLzUDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=a00149d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/M1R3Kq1ATYQ</a>"},{"pid":"1762c400e3c7bb7e2c51509f4825a6c729cba170","tid":767662,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":